    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="ca510-102"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.ContainerControl>类和类派生自它，如<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form>，可以自动调整自身大小，并根据当前系统字体或分辨率显示，其内容以每英寸点数 (DPI)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca510-102">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ContainerControl> class and classes derived from it, such as <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form>, can automatically resize themselves and their contents according to either the current system font or the resolution of the display, measured in dots per inch (DPI).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ca510-103"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.AutoScaleMode>枚举定义支持这些类和其派生的类型的自动缩放模式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca510-103">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.AutoScaleMode> enumeration defines the automatic scaling modes supported by these classes and their derived types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ca510-104">可以通过访问控件的当前模式及其<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ContainerControl.AutoScaleMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca510-104">A control's current mode can be accessed through its <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ContainerControl.AutoScaleMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ca510-105">大多数业务应用程序应使用的字体自动缩放模式。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca510-105">Most business applications should use the Font automatic scaling mode.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ca510-106">Dpi 缩放模式可用于基于图形的应用程序，与使用.NET Compact Framework 的默认缩放兼容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca510-106">The Dpi scaling mode is useful for graphics-based applications and is compatible with the default scaling used by the .NET Compact Framework.</span></span>  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="ca510-107">在.NET framework 1.0 和 1.1 版中，自动缩放已支持使用始终依赖于当前的系统字体的简单机制。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca510-107">In the .NET Framework versions 1.0 and 1.1, automatic scaling was supported using a simpler mechanism that always relied on the current system font.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ca510-108">此机制现已过时，但仍受支持的向后兼容性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca510-108">This mechanism is now obsolete but still supported for backward compatibility.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ca510-109">你可以通过设置获取较旧的缩放行为<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.AutoScale%2A>属性包含<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form>到`true`，它还将隐式将设置<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ContainerControl.AutoScaleMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>属性为无。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca510-109">You can obtain the older scaling behavior by setting the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.AutoScale%2A> property of the containing <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form> to `true`, which will also implicitly set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ContainerControl.AutoScaleMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property to None.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="ca510-110">相反，设置<xref:System.Windows.Forms.ContainerControl.AutoScaleMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>窗体的属性将设置<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.AutoScale%2A>到`false`，启用.NET framework 2.0 版引入的较新的缩放机制。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca510-110">Conversely, setting the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ContainerControl.AutoScaleMode%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property of a form will set <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form.AutoScale%2A> to `false`, enabling the newer scaling mechanism introduced with the .NET Framework version 2.0.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="ca510-111">请注意，对于智能手机应用程序，此枚举要求 Windows Mobile 版本 5.0 软件智能手机。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ca510-111">Note that for Smartphone applications, this enumeration requires Windows Mobile Version 5.0 software for Smartphones.</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
    </remarks>
